Job Details
Post:-Sales /Marketing Executives The company who is dealing with Automotive spare parts ( Both Car & Truck) in Dubai are seeking for Sales & Marketing Executives
Requirements
1)      Age - less than 35 years.
2)      Experience:- Minimum of 3 years in  any Auto spare parts establishment  from  UAE.
3)      Qualification: Graduate holder or above . 4)      Preferring UAE driving license. 5)      Salary package between AED 5000/- to AED.8000/- 6)      Should have an experience and knowledge in Import- Export market. 7)      Languages known: English / Hindi – Arabic also preferable 8)      Nativity from India or Srilanka. SEND YOUR RESUME WITH PHOTOGRAPH to the mail id of :-alrsales1988@gmail.com
